The evidence with the title 'Three Mile Island accident - Wikipedia ' says The Three Mile Island accident occurred on march 28, 1979, in reactor number 2 of Three Mile Island Nuclear Generating Station ( TMI-2 ) in Dauphin County , Pennsylvania , nearHarrisburg.It was the most significant accident in U.S. commercial nuclear power plant  ... It has been cited to have been a catalyst to the decline of a new reactor  ... 
